title: In the past 12 hours I have:
body:
wrote a 12 page paper (had research and sources done prior though)
collaborated with a group to complete a 6 page paper (associated with individual paper above)
finished my international finance homework (approx 45 minutes)
completed a 5 minute voice over PowerPoint presentation
created 1 unique post and 2 peer responses to a weekly discussion post
finished my Financial Modeling homework (approximately 30 minutes)

and you think you can procrastinate?

GOML
